WEBVTT

00:00:00.447 --> 00:00:01.955
Track 01.02

00:00:04.083 --> 00:00:04.535
Narrator: 1

00:00:05.928 --> 00:00:07.396
You argue with someone

00:00:07.484 --> 00:00:09.555
when you don’t agree about something.

00:00:11.654 --> 00:00:12.122
Narrator: 2

00:00:13.205 --> 00:00:14.264
You complain

00:00:14.289 --> 00:00:16.379
when you’re not happy about something

00:00:18.399 --> 00:00:18.883
Narrator: 3

00:00:20.514 --> 00:00:21.800
You encourage someone

00:00:21.904 --> 00:00:23.134
when you say good things

00:00:23.166 --> 00:00:24.658
about what they want to do.

00:00:26.543 --> 00:00:27.146
Narrator: 4

00:00:28.857 --> 00:00:29.734
If you persuade

00:00:29.759 --> 00:00:32.540
someone, you make them agree to do something.

00:00:34.568 --> 00:00:35.417
Narrator: 5

00:00:36.817 --> 00:00:38.523
If you insist on something,

00:00:38.858 --> 00:00:40.922
you say that something must happen.

00:00:42.877 --> 00:00:43.806
Narrator: 6

00:00:45.428 --> 00:00:47.106
You greet someone when they

00:00:47.136 --> 00:00:48.540
arrive at a place.

00:00:50.600 --> 00:00:51.195
Narrator: 7

00:00:52.659 --> 00:00:53.826
You admit something

00:00:53.937 --> 00:00:55.056
when you tell someone

00:00:55.081 --> 00:00:56.311
something about yourself

00:00:56.439 --> 00:00:57.494
that you don't want to.

00:00:59.680 --> 00:01:00.188
Narrator: 8

00:01:01.605 --> 00:01:03.228
You forgive someone when you

00:01:03.272 --> 00:01:04.915
stop being angry with them

00:01:04.940 --> 00:01:06.711
because they did something wrong.

00:01:08.722 --> 00:01:09.333
Narrator: 9

00:01:10.916 --> 00:01:12.279
You refuse to do something

00:01:12.304 --> 00:01:14.075
when you say you will not do it

00:01:15.944 --> 00:01:16.532
Narrator: 10

00:01:18.186 --> 00:01:19.984
You update someone when you give

00:01:20.028 --> 00:01:22.274
them the most recent information.